            <title>[HBASE-3441] Add means of graceful decommission of node where it sheds load slowly in a non-disruptive manner until its carrying none</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3441</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Needed decommissioning nodes.  Currently we effectively crash them out.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
